			a(href="/policy") Privacy Policy

		div#quotes
			div#quote1
				p “The ones who are crazy enough to think that they can change the world, are the ones who do it.”
				p - Steve Jobs
			div#quote2
				p “Education is what remains after one has forgotten what one has learned in school.”
				p - Albert Einstein
			div#quote3
				p “Education is the most powerful weapon which you can use to change the world.”
				p - Nelson Mandella
			div#quote4
				p “An investment in knowledge pays the best interest.”
				p - Benjamin Franklin
			div#quote5
				p “A well-educated mind will always have more questions than answers.”
				p - Helen Keller
				
			